title: Fast & Furious 9
description: Fast & Furious 9 follows Dom Toretto and his team as they face off against a dangerous new foe. The high-stakes action continues as the family fights for survival and justice.

title: One Piece Film Red
description: The Straw Hat Pirates find themselves in a battle against powerful new foes as they seek to protect an important item from the wrong hands.

title: Jujutsu Kaisen 0
description: Yuta Okkotsu, a young man haunted by the curse of his late childhood friend, seeks to understand and master the powers of Jujutsu Sorcery.

title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
description: Spider-Man faces challenges when his secret identity is exposed, leading him to seek help from Doctor Strange. The consequences create a multiverse catastrophe.

title: The Matrix Resurrections
description: Neo once again returns to the Matrix in a bid to escape from the simulated reality and find out what's real. With new enemies and allies, the fight continues.

title: Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings
description: Shang-Chi is drawn into the world of the Ten Rings organization, where he must confront his past and fight against enemies who have long controlled his destiny.

title: Dune
description: Dune follows the story of Paul Atreides, a young nobleman who must navigate political intrigue, control the spice trade, and survive on the dangerous desert planet.

title: Eternals
description: The Eternals, an immortal race of superheroes, emerge from the shadows to protect humanity from the ancient threat of the Deviants.
